        <mxCell id="itTbuPaQ1f0lpQnEGbCo-416" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;Step 3: Aggregate and Classify&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Now that the screenplays are sequence of encoded vectors, each screenplay is now a matrix of shape (num_chunks, encoder_dim), another transformer attempts to represent that as one vector of numbers before a linear layer projects it to logits for classification.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
